  "title": "Project Architect, Industrial Projects",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Architectural management/coordination with entire project processes including authority submission. (Industrial, Manufacturing, Institutional Projects)</li>\n  <li>Able to manage multiple projects independently.</li>\n  <li>Contract administration of construction projects to ensure project is built according to design intent and in compliance with building codes.</li>\n  <li>Liaise and communicate closely with client’s reps, consultants &amp; contractors.</li>\n  <li>Produce architectural drawings as directed and as required for project, in an effective &amp; professional manner.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Architecture from an accredited institution.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of experience especially in industrial projects.</li>\n  <li>Able to work under pressure in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and collaboratively.</li>\n  <li>Good communication and strong interpersonal skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If this opportunity aligns with your skills and experience, please submit your resume to <strong>koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Dickson KOH | Managing Partner<br>\nHead, Infrastructures Practice<br>\nEA Registration R1103367</p>",
